69
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:16,190
Smarter than you.

70
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:19,830
This is Xiaodao. You saw him last night.

71
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,040
Hello, Jian.

72
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,470
This building is a mess.

73
00:04:29,220 --> 00:04:30,750
Why do we need a new guard?

74
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:33,470
I know what you're up to.

75
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,110
Stop, Little Jian.

76
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,510
It's gone. Stop barking.

77
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:57,390
Jian, Jian.

78
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,550
What's gone? What do you mean?

79
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,630
Can't you see it?

80
00:05:12,660 --> 00:05:14,110
Jian, we're leaving.

81
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:17,830
Uncle Jian, goodbye.

82
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,950
Jian, see you.

83
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,480
Bro,

84
00:05:24,220 --> 00:05:25,950
