85
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,510
He can see things we can't see.

86
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,460
Come on. You go first.

87
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:47,120
Bro, I'm here...

88
00:05:47,970 --> 00:05:48,810
Auntie Mei.

89
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,880
Auntie Mei.

90
00:05:52,960 --> 00:05:55,230
Auntie Mei, I've told you many times

91
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,190
