93
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:06,230
It's on fire! On fire! Run!

94
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,230
Where's the fire?

95
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,270
Where's my whistle?

96
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,510
Are you looking for this?

97
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,590
It's too late!

98
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,030
What's too late?

99
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:21,790
