106
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,670
Come on, let's go upstairs.

107
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:40,800
4th floor.

108
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:43,800
You go.

109
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:46,510
